      <title>由 Bob Diamond 支持的 SPAC 签署合并协议，将 Events.com 上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/bob-diamond-led-spac-said-to-be-near-merger-with-events-com</link>
